http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170405&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=56523315</a><br />\n【暗交鄭俊弘】唔知對方有未婚妻？「受害人」何雁詩：其他嘢真係唔知咁多"},{"pid":"d19dc2fced4bf0e78a5f3b03c4e15ac9c5173146","tid":179900,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:39:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170405/2_496584_0/-%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%80%E6%96%B7%E6%AD%A3-%E7%99%BC%E7%88%9B%E6%B8%A3%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82%E5%88%AA%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF-%E9%84%AD%E4%BF%8A%E5%BC%98%E8%AA%8D%E9%8D%BE%E6%84%8F%E4%BD%95%E9%9B%81%E8%A9%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170405%2F2_496584_0%2F-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%25AD%25A3-%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2588%259B%25E6%25B8%25A3%25E7%2598%258B%25E7%258B%2582%25E5%2588%25AA%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E9%2584%25AD%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25BC%2598%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%258D%25BE%25E6%2584%258F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E9%259B%2581%25E8%25A9%25A9&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=1fe35737\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170405%2F2_496584_0%2F-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%25AD%25A3-%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2588%259B%25E6%25B8%25A3%25E7%2598%258B%25E7%258B%2582%25E5%2588%25AA%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E9%2584%25AD%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25BC%2598%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%258D%25BE%25E6%2584%258F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E9%259B%2581%25E8%25A9%25A9&h=5b38e659\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170405/2_496584_0/-%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%80%E6%96%B7%E6%AD%A3-%E7%99%BC%E7%88%9B%E6%B8%A3%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82%E5%88%AA%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF-%E9%84%AD%E4%BF%8A%E5%BC%98%E8%AA%8D%E9%8D%BE%E6%84%8F%E4%BD%95%E9%9B%81%E8%A9%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n在三月二十三日因為一張Uber收據，踢爆了鄭俊弘同何雁詩一齊渡過，搞到阿Beebs係屋企呆等到凌晨三點半。 <br />\n<br />\n之後兩日鄭俊弘不斷打電話俾beebs，但她拒絕接聽，直到廿七日終於再聽鄭俊弘電話，他不斷強調同何雁詩只係好朋友，叫beebs相信他們冇其他，而beebs亦一時心軟原諒對方，當晚更煲了湯入愉景灣。 <br />\n<br />\n「點知在中環碼頭，beebs同Fred撞到正，但係見Fred眉飛色舞喺度講電話，完全察覺唔到beebs喺度，一路講到返屋企，beebs坐同一班船，都估到佢一定係同Step傾緊，等Fred返上樓，beebs再上樓，準備開門之際，Fred衝了出嚟一見到佢仲講：『Hi baby, what are you doing here!』 <br />\n<br />\n「beebs問佢頭先同邊個講電話，Fred即刻好嬲，但係承認 同Step傾，佢話講緊公司啲唔開心嘢，之後beebs就叫Fred俾個電話佢睇，點知Fred發爛話：『No！』然後即刻刪除同Step嘅WhatsApp對話，beebs一手搶咗佢電話衝入廁所，睇到佢delete晒啲同Step嘅message，但係見到通話記錄大部分都係Stephaine Ho，佢問Fred如果冇嘢點解要delete晒啲對話，Fred就話：『驚你睇到唔開心。』佢兩個吵完一鑊之後，講到最後Fred終於親口認咗鍾意Step。」beebs亦徹底認清鄭俊弘真面目。</blockquote><br />\nn ben燈神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23183edf503253112292d74418bd49f03531c223","tid":179900,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比阿咩野弘食左啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：有日係愉景灣開工撞到兩個一齊放一隻狗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 何唔係有個圈外男朋友咩</blockquote><br />\n唔知，對佢既地既新聞冇留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再利申先：佢地果日冇拖手果類身體接觸架，<br />\n但你會睇到係一對情侶落街撚狗</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170405/mobile/bkn-20170405000058391-0405_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170405%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170405000058391-0405_00862_001.html&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f1af7ca1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170405/mobile/bkn-20170405000058391-0405_00862_001.html</a>真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7b6ecd7a12e5702c587679ca7446aec21945db9e","tid":179900,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquo